data.title: Guðmundur Þórarinsson
data.meta_description: Guðmundur "Gudi" Þórarinsson is an Icelandic professional footballer who plays as a left-back or left-midfielder for Armenian Premier League club FC Noah. He is also a well known singer in his homeland Iceland.
